What is Llama?

Llama is an open-source Large Language Model (LLM) developed by Meta that can understand and generate human-like text.

What is Ollama?

Ollama is a local runtime that downloads and runs LLMs such as Llama, Mistral, Gemma, and Qwen on your computer, enabling private and offline AI applications.

